Package: ggTag
Title: A package to allow ggplot2 or lattice graphics to be "tagged" with meta information
Version: 1.1.1
Author: Andy Nicholls <andyofsmeg@hotmail.com>
Maintainer: Andy Nicholls <andyofsmeg@hotmail.com>
Authors@R: person("Andy", "Nicholls", email = "andyofsmeg@hotmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A package to allow ggplot2 or lattice graphics to be "tagged" with meta information.  The primary purpose of the package is to take existing plots and wraps them in a grid fraemwork with metadata surrounding the plot.
Imports: 
  ggplot2
Depends: 
  R (>= 3.0.0),
	grid,
	stringr
Suggests: 
  testthat,
  lattice,
  png
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
